<bibRefCitation author="Smith, M. A." box="[553,687,510,536]" pageId="45" pageNumber="46" refId="ref34041" refString="Smith, M. A. (1943) The Fauna of British India, Ceylon and Burma, including the whole of the Indo-Chinese Subregion. Reptilia and Amphibia. Vol. 3. Serpentes. Taylor. &amp; Francis, London. 584 pp." type="book" year="1943">Smith 1943</bibRefCitation>
